Class QueueSecondary<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • components.queue.QueueSecondary<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Queue<T>, QueueKernel<T>, Standard<Queue<T>>, java.lang.Iterable<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Queue1L, QueueDL

    public abstract class QueueSecondary<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Queue<T>
    Abstract class providing the implementation of all of the layered secondary methods that were defined in the Queue interface, as well as the implementation for equals, toString, and hashCode methods.
    Author:
    Matthew Shoemaker
